title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 6 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 6 2022
description:
Sen. Mike Lee joins Clay and Buck to discuss his tight race in Utah against a Never Trumper posing as an independent. Fauci tells Stephen Colbert that we won't get back to normal until more people get vaccinated. Does anyone still believe this guy? Rep. Ted Budd, GOP nominee for Senate in North Carolina, joins C&B to talk about the importance of the midterms. Does Buck decorate for Halloween? Jesse Kelly feud continues. Protesting fan who ran on field files police report against Rams LB who tackled him.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
